snippet.title: Clash of Evil - Android Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching and Thanks for the support 
Don't forget to  Like and Subscribe 

Google play Download Link:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.WolfPack_Inc.Clash_Of_Evil&hl=en

App Store Games 
IOS Gameplay Download Link (iPhone - iPad - ipod touch):


Best Games and New games Every Day:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCe6AykcKVy5npMbk2X08GgA

Google+: https://goo.gl/wJNVeS

Clash Of Evil is the first action-packed fighting game, using the worlds scariest characters, such as Slender, Jeff the Killer, Sonic.EXE etc. Join online against friends using your favorite character to battle out and rise to the top. Prove who is the scariest of them all. Play Story mode to learn each character's journey. Change up your style and add color in Clash of Evil Store. More Characters and Maps will be available to play in oncoming updates.
